title: How the Past Has Affected Our Present
description:
This week, we take a look at Tasia and Camo's past and how this has influenced where they are in their lives now. Tasia and Camo discuss how having a criminal record made it difficult to find a job, but how it eventually led them to social media. On the flip side, they touch on how haters who can't let go of the past don't deserve a spot in their current life.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
